text: Ðæs <sind> þa engliscan landgæmere to Tantunæ.
To Risctune; Erest on Blacanford, ðanon andlang broces on Tan: ðanon andlang Tan on þa ealdan earace oð Beaddingbeorhbroc.

Upp andlang Beaddingcbroces on Beaddingcbricge: & ðanon upp andlang Halgan Wylles; & ðanon on <gerihte> on ða dic & ða norð andlang hrycges ongen þa twegen ðornas to broce, andlang brocrewe on Blacanforð.

Ðæt land wæs gebocod ðreora manna deg æt Nigon Hidum Wulfhere Ciddingce on þa gerat se þe landes bruce þæt he gesealde ælce gere xx scillingas into Tantune: & þæt hy fuligdon þam ðe ðonne ðere cyricean hlaford wære þa hwile þe hi landes brucan moton.

And þa lant gesealde Esne bisceop his mæge Deoreage & his magan Deneðryþe, æt Stoce & æt Rysctune ut of Tantune, on ða gerad þæt hy sealdon ælce geare twa dægfeorma into ðere stowe for Æsnes bisceopes sawle: & gyf hi þæt ne geleston, þa land gan into ðere stowe ðær hit togebyrað.
& þæt land æt Hegstealdcumbe Esne bisceop lende his mæge Wynsie on þa gerad þe ealle þa gerihta eodon into ðere stowe þe þæt land togebyrað, þæt is Tantun.
Ðis is þæt land to Cincgtune gemere.
Erest of Motleage, swa up on Hummapað, þonne adun on hearpað: ðonne on Finstowe, adun on Taccanlege westwerdre, ðonne on riht lanðsceare to Middelbroce.
Ðonne up on Bradanmed suðwerde, þonne on Noccanmere suðewerðe: þonne up on landsceare on biscopes gemere, ðonne up on Frecanbeorh, of Frecanbeorge eft on Motlege.
To Tantunæ: æræst þer Beaddincbroc scyt innan Tan, þanon to þam ealdan æsce, swa ðwyres ofer dune to þam oðrum esce, swa westwearð þæt hit cymð to Spænan.
Þanon to þere dene þe <man> het Orcerdcumb.
Ðanon gerihta ofer dune to þam ðyfele, þe man het Bradanðorn: þanon to þam ambran wege.
Þanon to Widecumbes heafde.
Ðanon andlang riðe to Eartancumbesforda.
Þanon to þere widan dic, & swa hit strecð westwerð on norðhealf ðes holtes þe <man> Duddincgbearu nemð.
Þanon of þere widan dic to Oterigcforda.
Þanon up agen stream oð <hit> cumð to ðes wulles heafde: þanon on norðhealf, oð <hit> cumð to Wiðigcumbe: swa forð to Ringwoldes hylle.
Þanon to Waldaneswege; swa to Oxenafelda.
Ðanon <to> Snellescumbes heafde: swa forð on gerihta to Greganstane & on westhealfe <Manhylle>, þanon to Blacanbroces wylle.
Swa nyðer andlang streames on ðone readan ford.
& swa <west> þurh þone holt oð hit cymð to Scytere: andlang Scyteres, on þone ealdan forð.
<Þanon> on westhealf on þone deoþan ford: ðanon to Heardangeate.
Þanon on suðhealfe on Bennascumbes riðe: swa nyðer on ðere riðe forðryne of ðere burnan on westhealf, oð hit <cymð> to Fyresleage.
Ðanon to Culfrandene, þanon forð to ðere stowe, þe man het Fiducscaga.
Swa <ðwyres> ofer ðone feld on westhealfe on Hafucalras.
Þanon on gerihta oð hit cymð to Tan ðære ea.
<Þanon> on westhealfe to Melenbeorgeburnan: swa norð oð Cyppanleage: þanon to Melenburnan.
Swa to þam haran ðorne, þanon norð ofer ðone feld westweard oð hit cymð to ðan halgan <æsce>, & swa west on þa ea wið Wifelescumbes gemere.
Þanon eft norð be ea oð ða ealdan gemerdic, ðanon to Pyttesforda: & swa on westhealf Lufesdune.
Þanon norð on ða ealdan streat & swa <ðurh> ðone norð del on gerihta to ðere frymwylle, þe man Wyllite namð.
Swa east on ðone <witan> mor.
Þanon to Lydegeard: þanon norð oð ða westhealfe ðes mores þe man het <Wullucesmor:> & swa on gerhita norð on ða ea.
Þanon up ongen stream on norðhealf oð ðone langan þorn.
Þanon <norð> ofer ðone feld, oð ðne ealdan ambran weg: & swa on norðhealf Truscumbes, swa on ðone <ambran> weg oþ þa sceortan dic.
Swa on easthealf on Ruganbeorg: of ðere stowe on norðhealf <Escholtes> on Horspaðesford.
Þanon suð on ðone horegan ford, swa on Heanwille.
Þanon on Gemotleage: swa on gerhita oð Dundic, þanon on Fiscwylle.
Swa to Ellewylle: swa on middel del þære dune þe man <Middelcnol> nemð.
Þanon on Hægelstalcumb & swa on Meccanfen: þanon to þere riðe, þæt man Neglescumb clypað.
Swa east on midneweardne del þære dune þe man Hætbeorg nemð: & swa be ufeweardum <Brigccumbe>, þanon on Leollescescumb, swa on Weannanstan.
Þanon on easthealf þæs mores þe man <Hafoc> ford nemð: þanon on Hægelstalcumb, & swa to þære stowe þe is gehaten Stantorr.
Þanon to <Secgbroce>, & swa on Tan þa ea, & swa be eastreame oð hyt cymð eft on <Beaddincgbeorh>.
To Wiþiclea; æræst on Ucingford, of þæs cumbes heafde on ðone smalan weg: <þurh> þone mor to Wiðigslede.
Þanon to Brocenanbeorge: swa to Wuduforda: þanon <to> Lullesbeorge.
Swa forð andlang hearpaðes to Megenstanes dene: <swa> to Wiðigleagate: þanon to Nædranbeorge: þanon ðurh þone mor be rihte gemere on Wiðigmor, <þanon> eft on Ucingford.
To Cearnæl; æræst of sæ up on Hengsterhricg: þonan norð on Gyrdweg: swa <norð> andlang hrigces on middeweardne Sealteracumb.
Þanon be cumbe <innan> Holanbroc.
Þanon andlang streames innan Hlosmoc: adune on <stream>, on Syfoneceras: þanon of streame eft onbutan Seofaneceras.
Eft suð on Hlosmoc: þanon adune on stream oð ða suran <apeldran>.
Þanon suð on þa norð rewe: þanon eft on Cern on <Gataford>: þanon suð bufan lytlan graf.
Swa suð on Earneshlinc: Of Earneshlince eft ut on <sæ>.
To Wecedforda; Erest on Keanulfesforda, up on stream on stangedelf: þanon <on> dic: swa east on Risclace.
Þanon on hearpað oð Brydanpytt: þanon west andlang forda.
Þanon <suð> on stream: þanon west on þelbrygce.
Ðanon norð on Heahbence eastewearde.
Þanon on ðone <haran> stan westanweardne: þanon norð on þæt ealde hlidgeat.
Swa norð on Hreodmere <easteweardne>.
Swa ut on sæ: of sæ on Wiðigcumbes heafod.
Þanon suð on Holandene: andlang denes <eft> on Ceanulfesford.
